OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain
OL,6,Fspreading slowly east to affect most
OL,7,Fareas overnight into Friday morning.
OL,8,FTurning colder with an increasing risk
OL,9,Fof sleet or snow over higher ground of
OL,10,Fthe Pennines.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FEarly rain easing into Friday
OL,13,Fafternoon, cloud perhaps breaking to
OL,14,Fgiving some afternoon brightness, but
OL,15,Frain returns into the evening. Feeling
OL,16,Fcolder by day under cloudy skies.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
