OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,6,Fdrier day likely Saturday, with some
OL,7,Fbrightness after a locally cool start.
OL,8,FConditions becoming cloudier and
OL,9,Fmilder into Sunday and Monday, with
OL,10,Flow cloud, fog and some rain returning.
